data.description:
Welcome to this beautiful home located in a lovely and friendly neighborhood. As you enter, you'll be greeted by a stunning living area with high ceilings and an open layout, creating a spacious and inviting atmosphere. This home features unique touches such as a skylight in the bathroom, a tray ceiling in the primary bedroom, and generously-sized bedrooms for your comfort.

Enjoy cozy family gatherings in the living area by the fireplace or make memories in the large backyard, which is enclosed by glass and screens for your convenience and privacy. The yard is also fenced, providing an extra layer of privacy and security.
